---
interface Props {
  spotsTotal: number;
  ctaHref: string;
}

const { ctaHref } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="section founding" id="fundadores" aria-labelledby="found-h2">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="tray">
      <span class="serial">§ 06 / Cupos iniciales</span>
      <span class="meta">Precio reducido · cierra al llenarse</span>
    </div>

    <div class="founding-grid">
      <div class="founding-intro">
        <h2 id="found-h2">Precio reducido para las primeras 2 clínicas.</h2>
        <p class="lede found-lede">
          Estamos documentando resultados en el nicho dental. Por eso abrimos dos cupos iniciales con un valor menor al
          precio estándar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="founding-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-k">Fee mensual</span>
          <span class="detail-v">$950.000</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-k">Setup inicial</span>
          <span class="detail-v">$500.000</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-k">Pauta publicitaria</span>
          <span class="detail-v alt">Aparte</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="founding-note">
        <p>
          Al cerrarse los dos cupos, el precio sube a la banda estándar de $1.150.000 - $1.200.000/mes. Sin excepciones.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="founding-cta">
        <a
          href={ctaHref}
          class="btn"
          id="founding-cta-btn"
          data-analytics-event="cta_click"
          data-analytics-location="founding"
        >
          Solicita una revisión gratis <svg class="arrow" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-arrow"></use></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .founding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .founding-intro {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1 / 4;
    }
    .founding-details {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 1;
    }
    .founding-note {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 2;
    }
    .founding-cta {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 3;
    }
  }

  .founding-intro h2 {
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .found-lede {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .founding-details {
    border: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
    background: var(--bone-2);
    padding: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .detail-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
  }
  .detail-row:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }
  .detail-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .detail-k {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--t-sm);
    color: var(--graphite);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .detail-v {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: var(--t-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .detail-v.alt {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: var(--t-xl);
    color: var(--vermilion);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .founding-note {
    font-size: var(--t-sm);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 55ch;
  }
  .founding-note p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founding-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
